      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy and honestly looks like it just left the dealership! It\u2019s in stunning condition, super clean inside and out, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to message me with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
