    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit with a meticulously maintained VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement. This chassis is structurally pristine, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to ensure torsional rigidity. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, mated to a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is further evidenced by a variable M differential lock and a suspension geometry refreshed with Bilstein dampers. With zero fluid seepage and compression numbers matching factory specifications, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience in a condition rarely preserved.",
