      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains taut and factory-fresh, showing no signs of wear, creases, or sun exposure. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians. Every switch and feature operates with the crisp precision of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually untouched example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
